HEADWORD: off-Broadway
<hw>off-Broadway</hw> <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to the
professional theaters in Manhattan not in the Broadway area; performed
in off-Broadway{1}.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

