==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: off-Broadway
<hw>off-Broadway</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A group of
low-budget theaters located outside the Broadway area in
Manhattan.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The professional drama presented in off-Broadway
theaters.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

